title: Walk to Shopping and Dining! Walk To Katy Trail
posting_body: ['Chic, contemporary spaces with a style that is comfortably at home in our Knox-Henderson neighborhood.', 'Each detail from the custom lighting right down to the built-in bookshelves - yes, built-ins! - has been thoughtfully included.', 'The amenities package is expansive and plush, offering multiple social zones, including a gorgeous pool deck and high-tech fitness studio.', 'A vibrant district of shops, restaurants and pubs lining the streets that remain as charming and walkable as they were decades ago.', 'Imagine leaving your apartment and strolling down to Henderson Street, where you get in a little retail therapy.', 'Window shop.', 'Try on clothes.', 'Get a new throw pillow.', 'Maybe have the lobster bisque for lunch and Toulouse Cafe.', 'You get the idea.', "It's a nice way to spend a Saturday in Dallas.", "Let's not forget about the Katy Trail which is so close to these new Knox-Henderson apartments that saying 'backyard' isn't really a stretch.", "Dare we say it's like a nirvana for runners, bikers, walkers and roller bladers who enjoy the easy connection to their neighborhood and beyond.", 'Please Call Desiree Mention ad D-194 Dash Apartment Locators', 'show contact info']
